UPDATE v2_job_status SET
                    flow_status = jsonb_set(
                        flow_status,
                        array['modules', $2::TEXT, 'agent_actions_success'],
                        COALESCE(
                            flow_status->'modules'->$2->'agent_actions_success',
                            to_jsonb(ARRAY[]::bool[])
                        ) || to_jsonb(ARRAY[$3::bool])
                    )
                WHERE id = $1
